SAE Standard Notice

This repository contains the public Structured Agent Exchange (SAE) specification.

Copyright (c) 2026 Structured Agent Exchange Contributors. Licensed under the Apache License, Version 2.0.

SAE is published as a small, neutral, versioned standard for sharing the shape of agent work across systems.

This repository includes:

- the public schema
- examples
- conformance guidance
- translation guidance
- evaluation materials for outside implementations

SAE can be implemented independently of any product-specific runtime, user interface, or private orchestration layer.
